message.content: The paper belongs to the arXiv CS sub-category "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language understanding and question answering. Other likely sub-categories could be "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) as the paper discusses neural network models, "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) as the models are based on the attention mechanism concept, "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval) as the paper deals with extracting information from a given context paragraph, and "cs.NE" (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as the models are based on neural networks.
